data.title: Hey, It's Chipotle
data.text: I always like Chipotle. I like the menu and the service. This is a typical restaurant in the chain, and it was accessible from my hotel.

data.title: Awesome as usual!
data.text: You just can't go wrong with stopping here for a quick and tasty Mexican meal.  I've ate at several of these places, and feel this one is as good as it gets.  The friendly staff and freshly made, delicious food makes this the perfect place to eat at.

data.title: One of my favorite fast-food chains
data.text: Chipotle is probably my favorite fast-food restaurant chain that doesn't feel like traditional (unhealthy) fast food. Simple and healthy ingredients and it tastes great. Good portions which should fill you up. OK prices. Highly recommended if you like Mexican food.

data.title: Fast Service but tiny burritos compared to other locations
data.text: Overall I think the service is fast and they moved the line pretty quickly. I will say that the 2 times I've been to this location I can tell you that they're a bit light on topping you with a good amount. Today my burrito was so small I made a comment at the checkout. They didn't do anything about it but this was no joke about half the size of what I get at other locations. I'm a bigger guy at 6-5 200lbs so I would probably avoid this location if you are a big eater. You shouldn't be hungry after an $8 burrito but I was. No issues with food quality however.

data.title: Always a good choice
data.text: The food speaks for itself. Always good and the service has always been great. I feel they do a good job of keeping the meat fresh and ready to go.

data.title: QUICK
data.text: This location was very quick and friendly. The food was hot and fresh. I would definitely recommend this location.

data.title: Always a great option
data.text: The staff are friendly and the food is top notch. Just like all other Chipotle restaurants. I have visited this store many times. The line is often long, just like all other locations, but they move you along quickly!

data.title: Typical Chipoptle
data.text: Longs lines, but they move the people along pretty good.  I usually get the steak burrito, but the meat was pretty tough last time.  Good food overall

data.title: Chipotle is my life!
data.text: What can I say?  It's Chipotle!  The latest craze in fast food.  This makes a perfect, well-rounded meal for lunch and/or dinner.  All items are fresh and tasty.  My favorite is the veggie bowl.  Chips and salsa are a must have.  Nice decor.  Friendly and professional staff.  Generous customers - had a "pay it forward" experience.  Made for a very nice experience for all, staff included.

data.title: Always reliable and heathly
data.text: Chipolte offers good food and fast service. High quality. I love their guacamole. Very much appreciate their Sofritos, which are vegan.

data.title: Excellent Food with No Ammentities
data.text: I love Chipolte for lunch when I'm in a hurry.  This is not a place to meet people and hang out. Furnishing and finishings are barely adequate, but adequate they are for a quick bite.  Good fare with no fanfare is what I am saying.

data.title: Great Quality Food
data.text: You can't beat a Chipotle burrito. This location is great and they provide fast service. They have had some new associates who are not very good with customer service and can be rude but usually it is only a quick interaction and then you can enjoy your amazing food. I would NOT use the online ordering system for this location. The websites claims you can just pick up the food and pay but the employees at this location make you go through the line while other customers order their food. The food was also very cold by the time you picked it up. It is also best to visit here during non meal times because I have seen the line out the door during dinner! Enjoy the great quality of food!

data.title: Good food - poor service
data.text:
We stopped going here a while ago when the staff changed.
Tried it again and the service is still poor.
The service is slow and not polite.
One server in the process was yawning and clearly didn't want to be there. Not one smile during the whole process.
If you try the 
9965 Hudson Rd.
Woodbury, MN 55125
store the food is as good and the service quicker and more polite.

data.title: Lines out the door make every mouth watering minute worth the wait.
data.text: I've never seen a day when the line isn't out the door for this healthy "fast food" place!  The choices are great, the meat is grass fed, the rice and beans are fresh.  I love Chipotle's, I'm making good choices to eat heathly foods.  It's busy but the line moves quickly.  Great outdoor seating.  We will be back!

data.title: Great for lunch
data.text: Chipotle is what it is, good  Mexican burritos, salad bowls, and tacos for a reasonable price. Can be a busy place, and the seating is at times limited.

data.title: food is terrible
data.text: the food is salty and the workers are dirty and have there hair in the food they need  hair nets. This is supposed to be fresh food  but the lettuce was rotten and the tomatoes were warm and mushy. avoid this crappy place . there are much better places to eat

data.title: Where is the Beef?
data.text: I ordered steak tacos and they told me they were out of steak. How can a franchise known for their grass feed meat be out of steak?
